<h1>Create an Article</h1>

#comment = deal with article model, rails provide form_helper method. form_helper makes creating and dealing with form very easy.

<%= form_for @article do |f| %>
    <p>
        <%= f.label :title %> <br>
        <%= f.text_field :title %>
    </p>

    <p>
        <%= f.label :description %> <br>
        <%= f.text_area :description %>
    </p>

    <p>
        <%= f.submit %>
    </P>

<% end %>